    <title type="html"><![CDATA[Apple Tart]]></title>
    <link href="http://et.github.com/blog/2012/09/25/apple-tart/"/>
    <updated>2012-09-25T14:45:00-07:00</updated>
    <id>http://et.github.com/blog/2012/09/25/apple-tart</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>I made this <a href="http://www.sophisticatedgourmet.com/2011/09/easy-fig-tarts/">recipe</a> with the last of the figs of the season.
Then I wanted to experiment with the remaining apples from our tree.</p>

<p>Pretty much follow the fig recipe verbatim except use sliced apples (coat lightly in lemon juice, 1 tbsp cinnamon, 1/2 tbsp nutmug).</p>

<p>Add a hint of cinnamon to seal the deal on presentation.</p>

<p><img src="http://et.github.com/images/apple-tart.jpg" width="500"></p>
]]></content>
